Roadmap (small tasks)
1. Back-end.
1. 1. Back-end: read day.
1. 1. 1. Change front-end invocation and content-type.
1. 1. 2. Parse, validate, error-handle, test invocation TEXT.
1. 1. 3. Touch test.sql. Create an example day in the database.
1. 1. 4. Return JSON (dictionary or null). Test it.
1. 2. Back-end: delete day.
1. 2. 1. Proper CGI end-points.
1. 2. 2. Parse request.
1. 2. 3. Execute queries.
1. 2. 4. Produce response.
1. 3. Back-end: update day.
1. 3. 1. Parse request.
1. 3. 2. Execute query.
1. 3. 3. Produce response.
1. 4. Back-end: create day.
1. 4. 1. Parse request.
1. 4. 2. Check day availability.
1. 4. 3. Check chore applicability (in regards to task schedule).
1. 4. 4. Check chore applicability (in regards to previous chores).
1. 4. 5. Produce day chores.
1. 4. 6. Produce response.
2. Front-end.
2. 1. Front-end: read day.
2. 2. Front-end: navigate days.
2. 3. Front-end: create day.
2. 4. Front-end: update day (chore.done).
2. 5. Front-end: delete day.
2. 6. Front-end: update day (chore.order_priority).
2. 7. Front-end: update day (delete chore).
2. 8. Front-end: update day (add chore).
2. 9. Front-end: update day (day.notes).
2. 10. Front-end: update day (chore.notes).
3. Deploy.

Roadmap (big picture)
1. Day CRUD.
2. Reliable hosting solution.
3. Mobile friendliness.
4. Statistics: day.
5. Statistics: daily.
6. Statistics: aggregate.
7. Task CRUD.
8. Category CRUD.
